---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/global/Breadcrumbs.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Services', href: '/services' },
  { name: 'Parent Support', href: '/parent-support' }
];
---

<BaseLayout title="Online Parent Guidance Consultation | Rabbia Psychologist" description="Online parent support and developmental guidance for behavior, routines, and child psychology concerns.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 max-w-4xl">
    <Breadcrumbs paths={breadcrumbs} />

    <div class="mt-8 mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Online Parent Guidance Consultation</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">Clear, professional guidance for parents who need help understanding their child's development, behaviour, or emotional needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Common Concerns We Address</h2>
      <p>This general consultation is the best starting point if you do not have a diagnosis but are noticing:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Frequent, intense emotional outbursts that disrupt family life.</li>
        <li>Refusal to follow basic daily routines (morning rush, bedtime, homework).</li>
        <li>Struggles with managing screen time and transitions.</li>
        <li>Questions about whether a behavior is "developmentally typical" or a sign of something else.</li>
        <li>Concerns about anxiety, shyness, or social interactions at school.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy">The Consultation Process</h2>

      <h3>1. Review</h3>
      <p>We discuss your primary concerns, looking at the history of the behaviour and the contexts in which it happens (home vs. school).</p>

      <h3>2. Education</h3>
      <p>I help you understand the developmental or psychological 'why' behind the behaviour, removing blame and focusing on skills.</p>

      <h3>3. Strategy</h3>
      <p>We co-create a realistic, step-by-step home plan. This isn't generic advice; it's tailored to your family's actual capacity and lifestyle.</p>

      <h3>4. Direction</h3>
      <p>If we determine that your child would benefit from formal assessment, therapy, or medical intervention, I will guide you on exactly what kind of professional to look for in your local area.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Session Structure</h2>
      <p>Sessions are 50–60 minutes and conducted securely online. After the session, you will typically be pointed toward relevant resources (like the <a href="/resource-vault" class="text-brand-trust">Resource Vault</a>) to help implement the strategies we discussed.</p>

      <div class="bg-brand-cream p-8 rounded-xl border border-brand-gold mt-12 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Get clarity and a plan.</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">Book an Online Parent Guidance Consultation (USD 85 / AUD 130).</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/book" class="bg-brand-navy text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-blue-900 transition-colors">Book Consultation</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="bg-white text-brand-navy border-2 border-brand-navy px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">View All Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
